+title = "Single Table"
+weight = 2
++++
+
+## Definition
+
+```sql
+SHOW SINGLE TABLE (tableRule | RULES) [FROM schemaName]
+
+tableRule:
+    RULE tableName
+```
+
+## Description
+
+| Column        | Description        |
+| ------------- | -------------------|
+| table_name    | Single table name  |
+| resource_name | Data source name   |
+
+## Example
+
+```sql
+mysql> show single table rules;
++--------------+---------------+
+| table_name   | resource_name |
++--------------+---------------+
+| t_single_0   | ds_0          |
+| t_single_1   | ds_1          |
++--------------+---------------+
+2 rows in set (0.02 sec)
+```
